WEBVTT

00:00.221 --> 00:02.794
What if you could empower your kids with the freedom they want...

00:02.901 --> 00:04.978
...and still have peace of mind that you and your child...

00:05.065 --> 00:07.089
...could stay connected from virtually anywhere?

00:07.377 --> 00:10.911
Amber Alert GPS is a new way to connect, protect and live.

00:11.297 --> 00:13.721
The small, lightweight smart locator device for kids...

00:13.830 --> 00:16.860
...gives children the freedom to call their parents through the touch of a button...

00:17.097 --> 00:20.103
...and parents the peace of mind with features like two-way calling,...

00:20.346 --> 00:24.378
...customizable safety zones, GPS and other location features...

00:24.578 --> 00:27.714
...that can all be monitored from the parent app on your smartphone.

